{"tid":1497892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今朝班黑警講到明香港之路舉行期間出嚟吠，你做初一我做十五聽朝大大力力錫春袋。","createTime":"2019-08-23T07:24:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T07:57:58.000Z","uid":167548,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"554aebdb8732d82aaa36514106417f31b281c8a5","tid":1497892,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:24:34.000Z","msg":"本身期待左823有得拖女女手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你班死黑警夠膽衝出嚟吠阻Q住晒，我聽日一撚定去機場博覽館睇清明上河圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身唸住晏就去觀塘就算鳩數，睇死朝早機場沒咩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但是你班黑警是要出嚟吠破壞期待已久嘅持手仔活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登仔一齊正評呢個Post同班死黑警講今晚谷住我道火，聽日就大大力力錫春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我要拖手仔啊</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你班死黑警我警告你咪撚阻住今晚和理非行動，否則聽日再錫春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全世界今日比班黑警搞到沒手仔拖嘅手足聽日一齊去睇清明上河圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e237a3fb4565129b78f2b33de041f0b78af90d8","tid":1497892,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:25:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef247c9064c6f295aa848b803e74c1ab7c030efa","tid":1497892,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:25:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c38f4278bd0a36b3c5f24c0f717d49d2c17741f","tid":1497892,"uid":154039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:26:34.000Z","msg":"今晚<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">823香港之路</span></span>！！！<br />\n麻煩各位巴絲幫手airdrop<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">比其他唔清楚既路人知發生咩事<br />\n呼籲參與！！！</span></span><br />\n請廣傳 好人一生平安！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TUtTraj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTUtTraj.jpg&h=68181c20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GCAVEvj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGCAVEvj.jpg&h=f04132bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a621b1ae1b7cc660fddc42ab991a9f1555385079","tid":1497892,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:28:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64c2fc10f1ceb87c3c359aac36bb5e6dd18f96c5","tid":1497892,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:35:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a88dc86500226c4caaf552b4ce84972ec85eb2c","tid":1497892,"uid":273252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:57:58.000Z","msg":"要大肆宣傳set 一個deadline.<br />\n講明<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>若果deadline前政府都唔回應五大訴求, 會行動升級</strong></span> 後果自負<br />\n<br />\n用意: 先小人後君子<br />\n1)迫使政府回應<br />\n2)市民有心理準備當日會有行動<br />\n3)令市民知道當天有行動係源於政府唔回應 <br />\n    (令佢地明白若果政府肯回應就唔會有行動阻礙到佢番工, 出街)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1) 五大訴求</strong><br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況, 解散、追究及重組警隊<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n[下一步棋] 救香港 Set Deadline 行動升級 (幫推)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1497453\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1497453</a>"}]}